# Requirements
## Introduction
  The aim of the project is to calaculate the numbers .The project has been used for addition,subtraction,division,multiplication.
## Research
It is useful for students and everyone to calaculate as soon as possible and it saves our timr

The main goal of our project is to provide various types of operations is used
   It should fulfill almost all the process for calaculation

